Second Department,

June, 1948.

(June 1, 1948.) Rosa De Giuseppe, as Administratrix of the Estate of Giovanni De Giuseppe, Deceased, Appellant, v. City of New York, Respondent.

Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals denied. Present — Lewis, P. J., Carswell, Johnston, Adel and Sneed, JJ. [See 273 App. Div. 1010.]
